I would like to return to that flow state which keeps me in high standards and shielded from most of the life's smaller issues, so that I can be above those things and keep on that vigour and zeal inside me, that Joy of Life, that amazing positive energy, that youthfulness, yes, that's what I want to be maintained inside me and not to get sucked into other mundane things in life. I want to be the name of joy and energy. I want to be the guy who knows how to bounce back, how to keep that momentum going.

Humanity itself has two repeated characters :

Struggle

and

Progress.

So no matter what we do, we will be in a good place once we have finished through the struggle.

This is your period of struggle, be happy for that. You cannot escape from this and you should not. Immerse yourself into this, let go totally go into the subjects, the knowledge, and the zone. You won't get another chance to get into things. So no matter what happens, you need to keep struggling and keep enjoying it at the end of a hard day's work. There would be many stops. Don't think there would be any less amount of learning. Just be your best self.

&nbsp;

Living The charged life.

Constantly engaging ourselves in a little bit uncomfortable situations, a little bit challenging situations and connecting each day to our best selves , progressing and going forward towards our best version - and with renewed enthusias, joy and satisfaction - enjoyiung the journey itself - That's the charged Life !

